.RH MOD.RECIPES-SOURCE ROCKET-SALAD SL "27 Sep 87" 1988
.RZ "ROCKET SALAD DRESSING" "A mild oil and vinegar salad dressing"
This is a mild and slightly sweet dressing.
I got it from my mother, who has made it for years.
.IH "1 cup" "1 cup"
.IG "1 Tbsp" "sugar" "15 ml"
.IG "1 tsp" "salt" "5 ml"
.IG "1 tsp" "paprika" "5 ml"
.IG "1 tsp" "dry mustard" "5 ml"
.IG "\(14 tsp" "pepper" "1 ml"
.IG "" "garlic powder"
.IG "\(14 cup" "vinegar" "60 ml"
.IG "\(34 cup" "vegetable oil" "250 ml"
.PH
.SK 1
Mix dry ingredients with the vinegar and shake well
.SK 2
Add the oil and shake again. Shake before using.
.NX
This gets its name from the red color the paprika gives the dressing.
It works best with mild mustard, if you can find any.
.SH RATING
.I Difficulty:
trivial.
.I Time:
45 seconds preparation.
.I Precision:
measure the ingredients.
.WR
